#### 4.1.2 Training details

This model was trained on a single 3090 GPU with the following hyperparameters:

* •

  Learning rate: 1e-5
* •

  Mixed precision training (fp16)
* •

  Number of training epochs: Table [3](https://arxiv.org/html/2412.17364v1#S4.T3 "Table 3 ‣ 4.1.2 Training details ‣ 4.1 Evaluation Setup ‣ 4 Experiment ‣ Efficient Fine-tuning Methodology of Text Embedding Models for Information Retrieval: Contrastive Learning Penalty (CLP)")
* •

  Per-device training batch size: 1
* •

  Gradient accumulation steps: 4

For CLP, the penalty weight was set to 0.1. For the MoE layers, the number of experts was set to 2 and the number of experts per token was set to 1.

